# What do we use your records for info page title
msgid "What do we use your records for?"
msgstr "¿Che mew kintukefiyiñ tüfachi wirin?"

# What do we use your records for info page content
msgid ""
"<0><0>Informing local authorities and landowners to help speed up the "
"erection of public warning signs.</0><br/><2>We use the data in scientific "
"research to get a better understanding of the timing and location of algal "
"blooms, to understand how climate change is impacting water quality now, and"
" to predict future impacts.</2><br/><4>We also use the data to support "
"environment agencies and water companies in water quality risk management "
"and prevention.</4></0>"
msgstr ""
"<0><0>Kimelaymi pu longko ülmen mew ka ti pu mülelu lof mew, kellüngeael ñi "
"zoy müchay zewma ngeael, ti pu maychikelu kom pu che. "
"</0><br/><2>Kuzaztukeyiñ kom zungü ti pu zoy kimlu mew tayiñ llowael kayiñ "
"zoy küme ententeam ti antü kañi chew mülen, ti pu rayen ke wezakefün kayiñ "
"kimael chum ngechi wezakemekey ti küme ko yem fewla, Tayiñ wüne piafiel "
"kümeke zungü. </2><br/><4> Ka kimkefiyiñ ka ke zungü tayiñ kellüael ti pu "
"füta ke lof küzawkelu ñi liftungeael zoy liftuael ti kümeke ko.</4></0>"

