# Verification message
msgid ""
"<0><p>Thanks so much for sending your record in - this looks very much like "
"a bloom of blue-green algae (also known as cyanobacteria), so we have "
"verified your record as “considered correct”.</p><1><p>These surface "
"accumulations constitute a high risk to public and animal health – "
"particularly to dogs. If this is a public place, then please check that "
"warning signs are posted. If not, please contact your local authority "
"environmental health officer or environment protection agency who can advise"
" the landowner on an appropriate warning sign.</p><p>Finally, please avoid "
"contact with the water or any shoreline scum. If you, or your pet, become "
"unwell after any contact with the water, we’d recommend you seek immediate "
"medical or veterinary advice.</p><p>Thanks again for using the "
"app!</p><p>The Bloomin'Algae team at the UK Centre for Ecology & "
"Hydrology</p></1></0>"
msgstr ""
"<0><p>Chaltumay tami werkulfiel tami pelon llüfken -fey ta ti weza karrü "
"kallfü lelu trokiley (ka kimniekey weza kütran külelu) tayu pefiel ti wirrin"
" kümelu trokilelu. </p><1><p> Tüfachi wezake zuam mongelelu rumi llikantuke "
"kom ti mongelechi che ka pu kullin, trewa ñiu zoy ñi kuñitukulnge ngey. "
"tüfachi füta wilngin mule peyum fetren che, pefinge ti pu pelom tulelu tami "
"kompafiel. Felenole fey pi afimi ti wünelelu longko ülmen ngune nielu "
"tüfachi zungu ti kuñil tukukelu mew kom lof pule ta ngülam tu afuy  ti ngen "
"külelu ka ti kuñultukulelu.</p><p> Fullkifillnge ti ko ka ti pu fillke poz "
"mulelu inaltu ko. Eymi ka ñi püchike kullin kütran le fullfilu ti ko mew. "
"Amufimaymi fey jka ti pu tremol kullin che fe mew. </p><p>Chaltumay tami "
"küzaw fiel tüfachi zungu! </p><p> Ti troy Bloomin alga de Centro de Ecología"
" e Hidrología del Reino unido</p></1></0>"

# Verification message
msgid "READ MORE"
msgstr "Papiltulenge"

# Verification message header
msgid "Info"
msgstr "Amulzunguwe"

# Verification message
msgid ""
"<0><p>Thanks for sending in your record using the Bloomin'Algae app. "
"</p><p>From your photos, we do not think this is blue-green algae "
"(cyanobacteria).</p><2><p>We cannot of course be certain that blue-green "
"algae are not present at all at this site, but they are not clearly visible "
"in the photo.</p><p>Our algal guide in the app has photos to help with "
"identification. Our website also has a description of a simple stick test "
"you can use to help eliminate duckweed and blanket weed, which are commonly "
"misidentified as blue-green algae: https://www.ceh.ac.uk/algal-"
"blooms/bloomin-algae</p><p>If you do suspect a bloom at any site, please "
"avoid contact with the water or any shoreline scum. If you, or your pet, "
"become unwell after contact with water that may be contaminated with blue-"
"green algae, we’d recommend you seek immediate medical or veterinary "
"advice.</p><p>Thanks again for using the app!</p><p>The Bloomin'Algae team "
"at the UK Centre for Ecology & Hydrology</p></2></0>"
msgstr ""
"<0><p>Chaltumay tami werkulfiel tüfachi zungu app bloomin algae. </p><p> "
"Tati pelom llüfken mew  zuamlafiyiñ ti karru kallfu lelu (weza kütran) "
"</p><2><p> Ta femngelay küme zuam layafiyin  tati kurru kallfu lelu ngelay "
"engun.</p><p> Tayin ngünelelu ti weza kuüran mew niey kiñe pelon llufken mew"
" tañi kelluniael ñi chem pingen. Tayin sitio web ka niey kiñe kintukun ka "
"kiñe falinonche zungu kiñe row kulelu tañi zuam afiel ka ñi kell afiel "
"nentungeael weza fün ko mew mulelu, weza kechi kimu keingun kimnoel chi reke"
" karru kalfu lelu reke: https://www.ceh.ac.uk/algal-blooms/bloomin-algae "
"</p><p> Kim rumefilmi kiñe rayen kulelu chem lof, mew rume fullkefillnge ti "
"ko ka chem rume poz inaltu ko. Eymi ka tami püchike kullin kütranle full "
"rume file ti ko, mutrumafimi tami tremol kullin kellu. </p><p> Chaltumay "
"tami kuzawel tüfachi zungu! </p><p>Troy Bloomin algae en el Centro de "
"Ecología e Hidrología del Reino unido </p></2></0>"

# Verification message
msgid ""
"<0><p>Thanks for sending in your record using the Bloomin'Algae "
"app.</p><p>We have rejected this record as we think the location is "
"incorrect. Please could you check your record and send in a new record with "
"the correct location.</p><2><p>Please see our website for further help with "
"using the app and identifying blooms of blue-green algae : "
"https://www.ceh.ac.uk/algal-blooms/bloomin-algae</p><p>If you do suspect a "
"bloom at any site, please avoid contact with the water or any shoreline "
"scum. If you, or your pet, become unwell after contact with water that may "
"be contaminated with blue-green algae, we’d recommend you seek immediate "
"medical or veterinary advice.</p><p>Thanks again for using the "
"app!</p><p>The Bloomin'Algae team at the UK Centre for Ecology & "
"Hydrology</p></2></0>"
msgstr ""
"<0><p>Chaltumay tami werkulfiel tami tüfachi zungu. </p><p>Zuamlafiyin "
"tüfachi wirrin yiñ kimnofiel ñi chumngen furreneafen kume ngüneltuafimi tami"
" wirrin kawerkulaymi kiñe we wirrin zoy kümelu. </p><2><p> Fürreneafen, "
"witranmange tañi lof web tami niael zoy kellun kami küzaw tuafiel tüfachi "
"zungu rayen kechi lelu ti kurru kallfū kütran https://www.ceh.ac.uk/algal-"
"blooms/bloomin-algae</p><p> Kim rumefilmi kiñe rayen kulelu chem lof, mew "
"rume fullkefillnge ti ko ka chem rume poz inaltu ko. Eymi ka tami püchike "
"kullin kütranle full rume file ti ko, mutrumafimi tami tremol kullin kellu "
"</p><p> Chaltumay tami kuzawel tüfachi zungu! <p> Troy Bloomin' algae en el "
"Centro de Ecología e Hidrología del Reino unido </2></0>"

# Verification message
msgid ""
"<0><p>Thanks for sending in your record using the Bloomin'Algae app. Your "
"photo is unfortunately not clear enough to make a decision.</p><p>Please "
"could you send in a new record with a closer photo of the water (if "
"possible, about 30-50 cm from the water surface and/or any surface "
"scums).</p><2><p>Please see our website for further help with identifying "
"blooms of blue-green algae : https://www.ceh.ac.uk/algal-blooms/bloomin-"
"algae</p><p>If you do suspect a bloom at any site, please avoid contact with"
" the water or any shoreline scum. If you, or your pet, become unwell after "
"contact with water that may be contaminated with blue-green algae, we’d "
"recommend you seek immediate medical or veterinary advice.</p><p>Thanks "
"again for using the app!</p><p>The Bloomin'Algae team at the UK Centre for "
"Ecology & Hydrology</p></2></0>"
msgstr ""
"<0><p> Chaltumay tami werkulfiel tami pelon llüfken tüfachi zungü boomin "
"algae, kütranngekechi reke tami pelon llüfken kümalay tami noael kiñe zungu."
" </p><p> Fúrreneafen werkulafuymi kiñe we wirrin ñi pelon llüfken zoy püye "
"lelu ko mew (pifulmi kiñeke 30-50 cm tañi chumte purram ti ko/chem rume "
"wente poz rekelelu)? </p><2><p> Fürreneafen, witranmange tañi lof web tami "
"niael zoy kellun kami küzaw tuafiel tüfachi zungu rayen kechi lelu ti kurru "
"kallfū kütran https://www.ceh.ac.uk/algal-blooms/bloomin-algae </p><p>Kim "
"rumefilmi kiñe rayen kulelu chem lof, mew rume fullkefillnge ti ko ka chem "
"rume poz inaltu ko. Eymi ka tami püchike kullin kütranle full rume file ti "
"ko, mutrumafimi tami tremol kullin kellu. </p><p> Chaltumay tami kuzawel "
"tüfachi zungu! </p><p> Troy Bloomin' Algae en el Centro de Ecología e "
"Hidrología del Reino unido</p></2></0>"

